      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0650P0-00812'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0650P0_20030623_GCR_62' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        The noble Baroness said: If the amendment is not acceptable to the Minister, I hope that lie will at least welcome the fact that I should be able to move it in a minute and a half.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0650P0-00813'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0650P0_20030623_GCR_63' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
