        <q>the subject of consultation with representatives of authorities and of staff before they are issued".</q>
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0650P0-00814'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0650P0_20030623_GCR_64' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
