        <ol>
        <li>(a) subsection (2) is omitted, and</li>
        <li>(b) in subsection (3)(b) after "common" in each case there is inserted "or open space".</li>
        </ol>
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0650P0-00927'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0650P0_20030623_GCR_177' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
