          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_57gc' title='Col. 57GC &mdash; HL Deb 23 June 2003 vol 650 c57GC' name='column_57gc' href='#column_57gc' rel='bookmark'>57GC</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0650P0-01051'>
        <a name='S5LV0650P0_20030623_GCR_301'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-jeff-rooker' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0650P0_20030623_GCR_301' title='Link to this speech by Mr Jeff Rooker' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
