          <p class='first-para'>
            We must wait until 7.30 p.m.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0650P0-01052'>
        <a name='S5LV0650P0_20030623_GCR_302'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/ms-joan-hanham' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0650P0_20030623_GCR_302' title='Link to this speech by Ms Joan Hanham' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/ms-joan-hanham" title="Ms Joan Hanham">Baroness Hanham</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            This is practically an example of filibustering. Would the noble Lord like to take us through the remaining 30 seconds?
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0650P0-01053'>
        <a name='S5LV0650P0_20030623_GCR_303'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-jeff-rooker' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0650P0_20030623_GCR_303' title='Link to this speech by Mr Jeff Rooker' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-jeff-rooker" title="Mr Jeff Rooker">Lord Rooker</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            I have a little Latin to quote to the Committee&#x2014;is it Latin or French? The lawyers will tell me&#x2014;to accompany my comment that this may be a convenient moment for the Committee to adjourn. I have heard the words <span class="italic">sine die,</span> but that means "don't ask me", whereas in reality I am adjourning the Committee until tomorrow afternoon.</p><p>
            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_58gc' title='Col. 58GC &mdash; HL Deb 23 June 2003 vol 650 c58GC' name='column_58gc' href='#column_58gc' rel='bookmark'>58GC</a>
            I apologise in advance for the fact that I shall not be present. The Government will be led by my noble friend Lord Bassam, ably assisted by my noble friend Lord Evans.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0650P0-01054'>
        <a name='S5LV0650P0_20030623_GCR_304'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/ms-joan-hanham' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0650P0_20030623_GCR_304' title='Link to this speech by Ms Joan Hanham' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/ms-joan-hanham" title="Ms Joan Hanham">Baroness Hanham</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            I should draw the attention of the noble Lord to the fact that the noble and learned Lord the Lord Chancellor has recommended that, in legal courts, the term <span class="italic">sine die</span> should no longer be used because no one understands what it means.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0650P0-01055'>
